  "text": "The SGD flux of each of the REEs to the Narragansett Bay/Rhode Island Sound was estimated following the same procedures described in [CITATION_1] for the SGD nutrient fluxes. Specifically, the volumetric flux of SGD (6.8 \u00d7 10 9 L yr",
